  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK560">
<l>āpayaṉ kuṉṟu maṟutoḻilōr nūṉmaṟappar </l>
<l> kāvalaṉ kāvā ṉeṉiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the guardian (of the country) neglects to guard it, the produce of the cows will fail, and the men of six duties viz., the Brahmins will forget the vedas.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
